name: Vapor Memories
description:
9/2013
Figured since I got back into shooting photos with the iPhone4 in 2021, I'd share some old photos from back when I used the iPhone4 as my primary phone for communication and digital photography. This was after my days at tumblr. Was on a job with my dad at some building in Virginia. Can't remember what building it was I use to be really bad with the drugs. I'm glad those days are over I don't miss that shit at all.
